SSA Gujarat CRC Coordinator Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 250 Vacancy

Total Vacancies:250

Name of the post:

  • CRC Coordinator 

Description:

The Samagra Shiksha Abhiyan (SSA) Gujarat issued a total of 250 vacancies for the posts of CRC Coordinator. The online application for these posts under SSA Gujarat shall start from 03-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 15-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for SSA Gujarat CRC Coordinator Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • Available soon

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 03-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 15-04-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have completed Graduation/ PTC/ B.Ed/ TET – I/ TET – II/ H TAT to apply for the post of CRC Coordinator 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 37 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per the 7th pay commission for the post of CRC Coordinator is INR 25000/-
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that SSA Gujarat issued this notification for which posts.

  • CRC Coordinator - 250

How to apply for SSA Gujarat CRC Coordinator Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of SSA Gujarat.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of the CRC Coordinator.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
